lyrics:
[verse]
Janamdin ki dheron shubhkaamnayein
Fano ke saath saath doobara hai ye din aaye
Chaar sau chauhattar saal ka jashn manayein
Khusiyon se bhare yeh pal hum saath bitaye

[chorus]
Janmadin mubarak ho, fano twenty-seven years
Aao milke manaye ye pyaara tyohaar
Gaao gungunao khushi se, sang sang hamari jeet hai
Janmdin mubarak ho, fano twenty-seven years
